interrogation.longDescription:
Generic multi tasking post for Brother Speedio M Series (M140, M200 and M300).
Use Turret 0/1 for +X axis turning.
Turret 202 for +Y axis turning.
Turret 203 for -X axis turning.
Turret 204 for -Y axis turning.
and Turret 205 for A90 +Y axis turning.
